<subSubSection id="FDAA651F06222E6EFF48FEB0FBE521B7" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="B50F369406222E6EFF48FEB0FBE521B7" blockId="8.[151,1437,854,1349]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis id="87C4EA8606222E6EFF48FEB0FED126F3" bold="true" box="[199,315,927,953]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">Remarks.</emphasis>
The carapace of 
<taxonomicName id="72B04D1706222E6EFD8CFEB0FD9126F2" authorityName="Poore" authorityYear="2004" box="[515,635,927,953]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Austrodromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="insignis">
<emphasis id="87C4EA8606222E6EFD8CFEB0FD9126F2" box="[515,635,927,953]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">A. insignis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is domed, covered in short spatuliform tomentum (
<taxonomicName id="72B04D1706222E6EFB44FEB0FAA426F3" baseAuthorityName="Rathbun" baseAuthorityYear="1923" box="[1227,1358,927,953]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dromiidae" genus="Austrodromidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="australis">
<emphasis id="87C4EA8606222E6EFB44FEB0FAA426F3" box="[1227,1358,927,953]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">A. australis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
not so strongly convex, covered in short coarse tomentum); the rostrum is tridentate, and the anterolateral margins of the carapace may have 1 or 2 small teeth (strongly tridentate, anterolateral border armed with several strong teeth). The CSIRO Database includes images of specimens taken from 
<collectingRegion id="7774F87606222E6EFCE0F924FBD1216F" box="[879,1083,1035,1061]" country="Australia" name="Western Australia" pageId="8" pageNumber="309">Western Australia</collectingRegion>
: Kalbarri, 
<geoCoordinate id="D084505306222E6EFB3CF924FAE8216F" box="[1203,1282,1035,1061]" degrees="27.8" direction="south" orientation="latitude" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" precision="5555" value="-27.8">27.8°S</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="D084505306222E6EFA81F924FA92216F" box="[1294,1400,1035,1061]" degrees="113.31" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" precision="555" value="113.31">113.31°E</geoCoordinate>
